properties.Name: BillingCycle
properties.Description:
The period upon which the Customer or Customer Account is regularly billed or statements issued.

Examples:
- Bi-Weekly
- Weekly
- Monthly
- Quarterly
- Annually
- Per Transaction
- One-time
- At time of event

Columns.Name: BillingCycleId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Billing Cycle.

Columns.Name: BillingCycleName
Columns.Description: The name of the Billing Cycle.

Columns.Name: BillingCycleDescription
Columns.Description: The description of the Billing Cycle.
